    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\">You pour out your life energy into a target, healing them at the cost of harming yourself. You take 30 negative/necrotic damage that cannot be resisted or reduced by any means, and your target is healed by twice that amount as positive healing. The range of this spell varies depending on the number of actions used to cast it; 5 feet for the 2 action version, and 60 feet for the 3 action version.</p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"> </p>\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><strong style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\">Heightened (6<sup>th</sup>) </strong>When you cast this spell, you can heal two targets within range by twice the amount of negative damage you’ve taken.</p>"
